member.summary:
Instantiates a new  with the given number of s.

For example, to create a  with 5  instances that point to temporary files, use this constructor and something along the lines of:

using (var ms = new MultiStream(typeof(FileStream), 5, i =>
{
    return new object[]
    {
        Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), $"multistream_test_{i}.txt"),
        FileMode.Create
    };
}))
{
    // ...
}
